Supported:
- click, click-and-drag pixels
- changing drawing color
- changing pointer size
- temporary eraser
- eraser can change in size
- delete all pixels
- Undo drawn pixels
- Undo erased pixels
- Add redo feature, make it same button as Undo button, but right-click to use it.



